<div class="popup popup-about">
  <div class="close-button close-popup">
    <%= image_tag "ast2.png", class: "close-ast", size: "30x30" %>
  </div>
  <div class="pmenu menu1 close-popup">
    <div class="aisatsu">
      <p>
      <div class="info">
        <p class="info-title"><%= image_tag "ast2.png", class: "close-ast", size: "15x15" %>Date & Time<%= image_tag "ast2.png", class: "close-ast", size: "15x15" %></p>
        <br>June 14th<br><br>
        14:40 Please come to the 4th floor of the main building.<br><br>
        15:00 Ceremony<br><br>
        16:00 Reception<br><br>
        <p class="info-title"><%= image_tag "ast2.png", class: "close-ast", size: "15x15" %>Venue<%= image_tag "ast2.png", class: "close-ast", size: "15x15" %></p>
        <br>Happoen Hakuhokan<br>
        1-1-1 Shirokanedai, Minato-ku, Tokyo 108-8631, Japan
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="pmenu menu2 close-popup">
    <div class="aisatsu">
      <p>
      Our concept for the wedding is <%= image_tag "ast2.png", class: "close-ast", size: "15x15" %>.<br>
      As you know, <%= image_tag "ast2.png", class: "close-ast", size: "15x15" %> means multiplication.<br>
      Multiplication often implies "fusion of two things" in Japanese context.<br><br>
      We will prepare many kinds of fusion like fusion of Japanese tradition and modern wedding, Mie and Kyoto (our hometowns), etc.<br><br>
      <%= image_tag "keyboard.jpg", class: "keyboard" %>
      <br><br>If you look at your Mac, <%= image_tag "ast2.png", class: "close-ast", size: "15x15" %> is located on the same key as 8.<br><br>
      Eight is considered to be a lucky number in Japan.<br>
      Coincidentally, August is the birth month of both of us, and eight is also the first kanji of the venue "Happoen (八芳園)"<br><br>
      You will find a lot of things that are shaped like either <%= image_tag "ast2.png", class: "close-ast", size: "15x15" %> or 8 at our wedding.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="pmenu menu3">
    <div class="list-block">
      <ul>
        <li>
        <div class="item-content">
          <div class="item-inner">
            <div class="item-title label">Your Code</div>
            <div class="item-input">
              <input class="invite" type="text" placeholder="Input 6 digit number">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        </li>
        <li>
        <div class="item-content">
          <div class="item-inner">
            <div class="item-title label guest"></div>
            <div class="item-input">
              <input class="guest-name" type="text" placeholder="">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        </li>
        <li>
        <div class="item-content">
          <div class="item-inner">
            <div class="item-title label">Ceremony</div>
            <div class="item-input">
              <label class="label-switch">
                <input class="attend1" type="checkbox">
                <div class="checkbox"></div>
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        </li>
        <li>
        <div class="item-content">
          <div class="item-inner">
            <div class="item-title label">Reception</div>
            <div class="item-input">
              <label class="label-switch">
                <input class="attend2" type="checkbox">
                <div class="checkbox"></div>
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        </li>
        <li>
        <div class="item-content">
          <div class="item-inner">
            <div class="item-title label">Message</div>
            <div class="item-input">
              <textarea class="message" placeholder="If you are alergic to any food, please mention it here." col="100" style="font-size: 90%; max-width: 100%;"></textarea>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        </li>
        <p class="my-button submit">Submit</p>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="panel-overlay"></div>

<!-- Left Panel with Reveal effect -->
<div class="panel panel-left panel-reveal">
  <div class="content-block">
    <ul class="menu">
      <li id="1" class="open-popup border">Date and Time</li>
      <li id="2" class="open-popup border">Concept</li>
      <li id="3" class="open-popup border">Attendance</li>
      <a target="_blank" href="http://happo-en.com/english/access/index.html">
        <li>
        Access
        </li>
      </a>
    </ul>
    <div class="keyboard">
      <div><%= image_tag "ast1.png", size: "50x50" %></div>
      <div><%= image_tag "8.png", size: "50x50" %></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="views">
  <div class="view view-main">
    <div class="page-content">
      <div class="content-block open-panel">
        <div class="top">
          <div class="top1">
            <p>JUNE BRI.DE</p>
          </div>
          <div class="top2">
            <p>JUNE 14TH 2015</p>
          </div>
          <div class="top3">
            <p>HAPPOEN</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-button open-panel">
          <div class="line"></div>
          <div class="line"></div>
          <div class="line"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="names">
          <p class="left">TAKAHIDE</p>
          <p class="right">MISATO</p>
        </div>
        <div class="chu">
          We will not look like this. It will be a Japanese traditional wedding.
        </div>
        <div class="top4 open-panel">
          <p class="click-here">CLICK HERE!</p>
        </div>
        <%= image_tag "kekkon.png", class: "top-image" %>
        <%= image_tag "kekkon_black.png", class: "top-image black" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript">
$(".page-content").snowfall({
flakeCount :20, // 数
flakeIndex : 99999, // スタイルシートのz-indexの値
maxSpeed : 3, // 最大速度
minSpeed : 1, // 最小速度
